Class LibraryMemberTest

java.lang.Object
LibraryMemberTest
public class LibraryMemberTest extends Object
Unit tests for the LibraryMember class.

Tests the functionality of the constructor, getter, setter, and methods related to managing borrowed books, such as adding to and returning from the borrowed books list. Also tests the getDetails and printDetails methods.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Neil Hutton
